{"tid":2498991,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"自稱流浪動物搜索隊，IG籌旗五萬，但無法任何詳細資料！？","createTime":"2021-04-21T14:07:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T18:12:34.000Z","uid":105678,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"81393368f325fde48738516fca2163951fee9db4","tid":2498991,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:07:15.000Z","msg":"<strong>借朋友ac出post，帳號持有人不持有任何立場</strong><br />\n<br />\n收到自稱係幫助流浪動物搜索隊嘅dm，話希望幫佢出post叫人幫手follow佢個page，同埋捐款幫咗一隻癱瘓狗狗。 <br />\n<br />\n 我涉及錢銀嘅時候變得好謹慎，睇返對方profile。而家喺度為一隻癱瘓左嘅狗隻籌款五萬蚊，再睇真啲嘅時候眼都突埋，個post入邊得一張相同埋一段15秒左右嘅片。<br />\n<br />\n最基本嘅醫生紙、獸醫診所地址，其他任何資料都欠奉。最離奇嘅係個post set咗唔俾留言。<br />\n<br />\n再睇返佢出嘅其他post都冇禁止人留言，睇到呢度嘅時候，我充滿疑惑向post索求醫生紙同埋獸醫診所地址。 結果佢同我講： 我都唔知問緊網友。<br />\n<br />\n我就差啲屌出聲。post主幫手籌款左三日，結果咩都唔知嘅情況下，就想籌5萬銀。現階段唔係想話質疑對方係咪想呃錢。  只係話就算籌款都好可唔可以花多啲心機同功夫，完全冇做過任何Fact check，就利用自己嘅公信力做抵押，涉及錢銀嘅嘢可唔可以唔好咁兒戲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXhKE3MKBbcTfoe6TLXjneaXAPGKFebY8s2gfypqYjto4?filename=Fu6k53P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFu6k53P.jpg&h=0fbf033d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRJDwMZBDkSSCYzDFsCiAGmB5Jum3ENcpG3WLVb5pNXu6?filename=OoZZCaQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOoZZCaQ.jpg&h=80541565&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmP4eZQgTsoEZzaZ4NrCWz66KzFfYbumNVGnZj4CXdNyN1?filename=vbgJjoY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvbgJjoY.jpg&h=4ee7d5f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">到10點截稿前仍然未公布醫生紙同埋獸醫診所地址</span></strong>"},{"pid":"bbe47abcf7dba130b026d4e95392512e1c914292","tid":2498991,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:23:37.000Z","msg":"籌左6k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0c7b53eac6fba55966b63b3b129bf6e16be0c0b","tid":2498991,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,